                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230514-69-off370 t18230514-69-crimeloc373"></join>. The prisoner took a furnished room on my second floor, a few weeks before Christmas, at 5 s. a week - he remained there till the 9th of April; he was apprehended on another charge, and on examination we missed the property - he owed four weeks' rent; he said he was in town on a law suit.</p>
